<p><span class="anchor" id="p35"></span>• وهب بن سفيان.<a href="#p35" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p36"></span><span class="c5">عن:</span> بيان عن قيس عن أبي سهم.<a href="#p36" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p37"></span><span class="c5">وعنه:</span> شاذان.<a href="#p37" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
